%% Diagram: Vector Clock Trace
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant P1
    participant P2
    participant P3

    Note over P1: [1,0,0]
    P1->>P2: [1,0,0]
    Note over P2: [1,1,0]
    Note over P3: [0,0,1]
    Note over P3: [0,0,2]
    P2->>P3: [1,1,0]
    Note over P3: merge [1,1,3]
    P1->>P2: [2,0,0]
    Note over P2: merge [2,2,0]

    Note right of P3: P2 [2,2,0] and P3 [1,1,3] are concurrent: 2>1 but 0<3.
